  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"rdtqvhQY\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=358597125&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E5%88%BB%E6%9D%BF%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">性别刻板印象<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>是在给男性和女性“定型”，男性应该这样，女性就应该那样。对于这种“定型”，当作玩笑就好，千万不要当真。</p><p data-pid=\"k8qliklu\">现实生活是多元化的，男性和女性在生活中的角色也是多样化的。</p><p data-pid=\"Oaj6Ed59\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=358597125&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%94%B7%E4%B8%BB%E5%A4%96&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">男主外<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span> = 赚钱养家。</p><p data-pid=\"Aae-NKZJ\"><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=358597125&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%A5%B3%E4%B8%BB%E5%86%85&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">女主内<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span> = 带小孩，洗衣做饭家务全包。</p><p data-pid=\"1CfXNuFR\">程序员 = 木讷男+格子衫+秃头</p><p data-pid=\"rOr_DSme\">开车技术不行，出事故 = <span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=358597125&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%B8%E6%9C%BA&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">女司机<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span></p><p data-pid=\"obdkElR_\">护士 = 女护士</p><p data-pid=\"nowlCrG2\">医生 = 男医生</p><p data-pid=\"xvVpQnlB\">年轻女性开豪车 = 被包养</p><p data-pid=\"PWPQneHZ\">······</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-bfebf0f29e47153e4704f7d467b9b055_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"395\" data-rawheight=\"125\" data-original-token=\"v2-c1658f48ca99c2e1f0e812a9a6f48dbe\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3813a86f0fc54b29f85eeaddab321dc0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"395\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='395' height='125'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"395\" data-rawheight=\"125\" data-original-token=\"v2-c1658f48ca99c2e1f0e812a9a6f48dbe\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3813a86f0fc54b29f85eeaddab321dc0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"395\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-bfebf0f29e47153e4704f7d467b9b055_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"YieixzBw\">这种不以事实为基础的印象，不要也罢。</p><p data-pid=\"29E6tGaa\">造成这种刻板印象的根本原因就是认知的不足，容易偏信偏听，道听途说却被认定为事实的真相。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
  "excerpt": "性别刻板印象是在给男性和女性“定型”，男性应该这样，女性就应该那样。对于这种“定型”，当作玩笑就好，千万不要当真。\n\n现实生活是多元化的，男性和女性在生活中的角色也是多样化的。\n\n男主外 = 赚钱养家。\n\n女主内 = 带小孩，洗衣做饭家务全包。\n\n程序员 = 木讷男+格子衫+秃头\n\n开车技术不行，出事故 = 女司机\n\n护士 = 女护士\n\n医生 = 男医生\n\n年轻女性开豪车 = 被包养\n\n······\n\n这种不以事实为基础的印象，不要也罢。\n\n造成这种刻板印象的根本原因就是认知的不足，容易偏信偏听，道听途说却被认定为事实的真相。",
